          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use this property to request special handling of the audio and video on the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "FaceTime call. For example, you might request video mirroring to simplify",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "activities that involve left-right movement. The system respects your preferences",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "when possible, but may override those preferences if system- or user-specific",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "settings are present. The default value of this property is an empty set.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
